35	- [ ] `seed_wc2026(result, teams)` returns each team's latest historical rating, defaulting to `initial_rating` for teams absent from history.
36	- [ ] `EloConfig` defaults load; invalid values (non-positive K / initial_rating, negative home_advantage) raise `ValidationError`; `AppConfig().elo` is an `EloConfig`.
37	- [ ] All tests pass
38	- [ ] SOLID, clean code (methods < 10 lines, classes < 50 lines, files < 500–600 lines), TDD
